    "ChatGPT's capabilities are based on a Generative 2 During our manual classification of our validation set, it took us around one minute per sentence.",
    "Thus, given the sample of two million sentences, it would take around 33,000 hours or almost 4 years cumulative to classify the entire dataset manually.",
